Class ReversalAmount

    java.lang.Comparable<ReversalAmount>

    public final class ReversalAmount
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<ReversalAmount>
    The class indicates the amount of price movement required to shift a chart to the right. This condition is used on charts that only take into consideration price movement instead of both price and time. Is used for Point and Figures charts for example.
